OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter woman in 60s stabbed
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after a woman in her 60s was
OL,8,Fstabbed multiple times in Bicester.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to an address in
OL,11,FFair Close on Friday, March 27th,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of an incident.
OL,14,FMichael Brits, aged 27, of Fair Close,
OL,15,Fhas now been charged with one count
OL,16,Feach of attempted murder, possession
OL,17,Fof a bladed article in a public place,
OL,18,Fthreatening a person with a bladed
OL,19,Farticle and outraging public decency.
