OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter woman in 60s stabbed
OL,6,FThe victim suffered multiple stab
OL,7,Fwounds and has been discharged from
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FBrits has been remanded to appear at
OL,11,FMilton Keynes Magistrates' Court on
OL,12,FMonday, March 30th
